title: Kerala Tourist Places | Best Places To Visit in Kerala
description:
Kerala Tourist Places | Best Places to Visit in Kerala 

About this video:

This video is about the best tourist places in Kerala. Kerala is an exceptional Indian state that is filled with natural beauty, historical places, cultural heritage and tons of tourist places. Be it the Alleppey's backwaters or  Wayanad's mountains, Kovalam's beaches or Munnar's tea plantation Kerala has something for every kind of traveller.
